                                            <p><a href="" class="rg-label level" style="background-color: #820;">方丈郡伯</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;600-1000</p>
                                            <p><a href="" class="rg-label level" style="background-color: #FAD;">方丈郡侯</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;1000-1500</p>
                                            <p><a href="" class="rg-label level" style="background-color: #60f;">方丈郡公</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;1500-2100</p>
                                            <p><a href="" class="rg-label level" style="background-color: #900;">方丈阁伯</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;2100-2800</p>
                                            <p><a href="" class="rg-label level" style="background-color: #2AA;">方丈阁侯</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;2800-3600</p>
